Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,淚的咆哮 你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是…鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種壓迫感是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那紅色的查克拉又是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…是怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會說 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不把你送給大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會說 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把你的手腳給折斷 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.豪火球之術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該清醒點了吧 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是還沒清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把你打到動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後帶你回去 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真羅嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這既沒父母也沒兄弟的混小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能體會我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小就孤單一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底能明白些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有著親情的羈絆 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了他們之後的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎麼能明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不瞭解真正的父母兄弟之情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我請客 你就放開吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和伊魯卡老師在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾想像過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做忍者還是得先填飽肚子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別乘機大吃一頓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有爸爸 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否就是這樣的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊 你這拖後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會輸給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你怎麼說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想兄弟或許就是這種感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會如此對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是好不容易得來的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…一定要阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會再回頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來斬斷這份羈絆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要斬斷這份羈絆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼到現在還戴著護額
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認 你是很強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和我一樣都瞭解孤獨的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這份痛苦 會讓人變得堅強起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此 我才要斬斷這份羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而得到更為強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始 我要和你平等對決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無法傷到我額頭的一分一毫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點是永遠不會改變的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來和你說什麼都是白費口舌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒聊就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後 你我之間只有戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才一直無法捕捉的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看清了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助的動作和之前完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 決不能輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為身體漸漸習慣了咒印狀態的緣故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙移動的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身微妙的力道分佈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他的下一個動作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚地浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有此眼力 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會白白浪費查克拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為咒印實在太消耗體力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我只要掌握先機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對準此刻看到的鳴人之後的動作…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的動作完全被他看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這條路沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有種不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.龍火之術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好強…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都晚了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經晚了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你真夠弱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大爺我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:15:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再感謝一下把我封印在\N你這種小鬼體內的第四代火影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經看穿了鳴人的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他身上的查克拉卻做出了不同的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去查克拉好像有意識自己在動一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我的眼睛也無法看透
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股紅色的查克拉 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非尋常的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標果然是鳴人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的組織曉所下達的至上命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你小子有著特別的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我總算明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.豪火球之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那種查克拉保護著他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持距離作戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就抓不到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躲開就很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦借用了這股力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後會變成什麼樣我也不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也沒辦法啊 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比你更特別
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 身體好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 左手幾乎毫無感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這股力量並不能一直用下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的一擊 就是最後的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚雨的終結
